originalText.text:
Dr. Felix is incredible!! It has been about one year of lessons with him and my vocal skills have improved tremendously. Dr. Felix taught me a compassionate way of approaching my singing and helped me get through many restrictions to have a beautiful voice.  He is extremely knowledgeable, quick and always knows the right exercise for me to get my voice to the next level in its development and refinement.

I am amazed by how fast my voice has developed with his lessons.  Dr. Felix has caused me to find more self confidence, structure and skill as a lead singer for my band. Dr. Felix is a strong advocate for my voice and self expression as an artist. I am so thankful to take lessons with him. I definitely recommend him!!

originalText.text:
I really cannot say enough good things about Singing Lessons NYC.  From day 1 Ellie and Hazel were amazing at putting me at ease, answering my beginner's questions, and connecting me with the right instructors.  They really go out of their way to create a welcoming environment for new singers (and experienced singers too I'm sure).

The school also has some really amazing instructors.  I am working with Taylor right now, and he's a marvel. I am really astounded by the progress that I have made since we began working together, and I put most of that down to Taylor's ability to patiently iterate on new approaches with me, looking for ones that fit my voice, my place in my singing journey and my learning style.  I feel like this is the most progress that I have made in a long while, and now I have all of these new areas of my voice to continue to explore.  This is exactly what I was looking for.

Highly recommended!

originalText.text:
Love, LOVE, LLLOOOVE my lessons with Dr Felix!  I’ve taken lessons at Singing Lessons NYC other location in the Garment District but when Felix started teaching out of this Columbus Circle location, it was a lot closer to my apartment

Dr. Felix is so positive but still gives a lot of very useful information and techniques and has helped me a lot to feel more comfortable with my voice.  I’ve been taking singing lessons at Singing Lessons NYC for a while but Dr Felix is a new teacher for me and he is outstanding!

I highly recommend Singing Lessons NYC Columbus Circle and especially Dr Felix to anyone who wants to take their singing to the next level!

originalText.text:
I can't recommend Singing Lessons NYC highly enough.  Ellie literally changed my life!  I started taking lessons with her 10 years ago and have continued on and off through that time and I love that lady :)

She has prepared me for musical theatre class and auditions and my partner and I even ended up releasing a single!  Something that would have been unthinkable without her amazing guidance.  She is also an incredible person - kind, funny and ALWAYS SO encouraging.  So many people have been told they can't sing or have fear around singing - Ellie will show you that you CAN sing.  She really is amazing.  Seriously, one class with her will make a huge difference to your life.
